hackathon-description-text: Royal Hackaway is a 24 hour student hackathon hosted at Royal Holloway on the 13th to the 14th of January 2018 where the most creative inventors, desginers and programmers come together and make awesome projects!
hackathon-rules: You can find our rules and code of conduct

hackathon-prizes.prize-title: Amazon Web Services - Best Use of AWS
Best IoT Hack Using a Qualcomm Device

hackathon-judging-criteria.judging-criterion: We're looking for cool projects, preferably with some open data :) Be proud of showing what you've achieved, even if you didn't meet all your goals!
